{"tid":831100,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"圍棋推廣／討論區（1）","createTime":"2018-09-21T16:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T14:52:17.000Z","uid":125720,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"634065bf975db4f74498394fff02490bbe6d5482","tid":831100,"uid":125720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"自己都好鍾意捉 希望多啲人嚟討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n棋力3～4段，歡迎分享棋譜，可以幫手覆盤，2段以下有問題我都應該可以指點一二，再高段就唔好搵我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自學渠道</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n101圍棋網<a href=\"https://www.101weiqi.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.101weiqi.com%2F&d=RWxHtKKjDDt9mVk%2FDQYX%2BEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=bc297b71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.101weiqi.com/</a><br />\n搵局部行法，做題目都好用。<br />\n<br />\n奕客圍棋<a href=\"http://www.yikeweiqi.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yikeweiqi.com%2F&d=RWxHtKKjDDt9mVk%2FDQYX%2BEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=74d116ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.yikeweiqi.com/</a>（有手機app）<br />\n可以非即時對局（10日1步），可以返工返學／得閒先行棋，有直播賽事解說同死活題。<br />\n<br />\n野狐圍棋（騰訊）<a href=\"https://www.foxwq.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxwq.com%2F&d=RWxHtKKjDDt9mVk%2FDQYX%2BEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=13bec22c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxwq.com/</a><br />\n線上捉棋最多人用，同樣有直播解說，職業棋手經常使用，有絕藝（AI）覆盤。<br />\n<br />\nyoutube channel 高川格<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC4H1BXlBM8UdPFnw0L9potQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC4H1BXlBM8UdPFnw0L9potQ&d=RWxHtKKjDDt9mVk%2FDQYX%2BEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f56cb58e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC4H1BXlBM8UdPFnw0L9potQ</a><br />\n個人認為佢講得幾好。<br />\n<br />\n圍棋tv<a href=\"https://www.weiqitv.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weiqitv.com%2F&d=RWxHtKKjDDt9mVk%2FDQYX%2BEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e96d9661\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weiqitv.com/</a><br />\n入面好多唔同片講棋，但登入嗰啲好煩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>常見問題</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n邊度可以學棋？自學得唔得？<br />\n棋院上堂會進步得有效率啲，自學嘅話最好有一定水平，網上資源對初學者幫助比較少同唔全面（死活一堆但難訓練棋形處理／佈局／官子／厚薄）。<br />\n<br />\n點可以訓練佈局／中盤／官子？<br />\n多啲擺譜針對大局觀；中盤要多啲捉棋培養棋感，之後覆盤；官子就多啲做題目。"},{"pid":"79c071a67e5dd7217cf2dfcdde7fa249f084dd4a","tid":831100,"uid":125720,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6408ffb988daedb6b5eb667e15e6049482ff30d9","tid":831100,"uid":34001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:20:27.000Z","msg":"幫推，有一段時間冇捉lu<br />\n之前2段，而家唔知仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f42a65632d453bf53233a6733aec3c192ae96d","tid":831100,"uid":53805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:23:25.000Z","msg":"9路棋開局有咩推薦?<br />\n<br />\nfeels rating 卡5k"},{"pid":"3444915bfceb6c8061fe67fb638343849af2ce55","tid":831100,"uid":53805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"59f42a65632d453bf53233a6733aec3c192ae96d","tid":831100,"uid":53805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:23:25.000Z","msg":"9路棋開局有咩推薦?<br />\n<br />\nfeels rating 卡5k"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"leela*"},{"pid":"e5a63f03019ec3bc8f8a7a262924f2b7d3333ca5","tid":831100,"uid":125720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3444915bfceb6c8061fe67fb638343849af2ce55","tid":831100,"uid":53805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"59f42a65632d453bf53233a6733aec3c192ae96d","tid":831100,"uid":53805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:23:25.000Z","msg":"9路棋開局有咩推薦?<br />\n<br />\nfeels rating 卡5k"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"leela*"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:49:12.000Z","msg":"無研究9路<im