:3,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T09:59:42.000Z","msg":"呢個興趣要花太多時間，好難維持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf69eb26a90813f561168da6c3bf7855425b2110","tid":831100,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"665ec77bbb867b9dcb00851874e5f8ef1923939b","tid":831100,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T09:59:42.000Z","msg":"呢個興趣要花太多時間，好難維持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"睇你要去到咩程度先叫滿足啫<br />\n<br />\n上次去日本梅田圍棋沙龍 大把老人家喺度玩 但佢地又唔會好在意點贏點輸"},{"pid":"8522915b1759fced64d16322bbc2dd1a8b63dd50","tid":831100,"uid":125720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"665ec77bbb867b9dcb00851874e5f8ef1923939b","tid":831100,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T09:59:42.000Z","msg":"呢個興趣要花太多時間，好難維持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"難唔難維持依啲嘢好個人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得閒上網捉吓棋都可以好有趣，唔一定要太執著棋力進步<br />\n<br />\n但客觀黎講宜家玩棋的確需要更多時間<br />\n圍棋本身入門門檻高，其他棋類大部分已經變晒背譜（象棋，國際象棋，五子棋）<br />\nAlphaGo出現之後圍棋脫離咗背譜嘅模式，流行變化宜家仲一路變緊"}]}